I made a small change to `ctrl/social.js` to test whether I can play a game of chess with folks who don't follow me, but now Patchbay keeps hanging after a few minutes of use for no discernable reason. I'm *hoping* it's unrelated, but I wanted to post just on the off chance that I've triggered some sort of bug.

Before:

```
return following.filter(function(n) {
  return followedBy.indexOf(n) !== -1;
});
```

After:

```
return following;
```

Was this a Bad Idea? :innocent:
